1
00:01:22,767 --> 00:01:25,642
<i>Code Blue, Neurosurgery. Code Blue.</i>

2
00:01:25,642 --> 00:01:30,547
<i>All available neurosurgery personnel
to the VIP ICU.</i>

3
00:01:30,547 --> 00:01:33,112
<i>Code Blue, Neurosurgery. Code Blue.</i>

4
00:01:33,112 --> 00:01:38,358
<i>All available neurosurgery personnel
to the VIP ICU.</i>

5
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,071
Get the defib, now!

6
00:01:57,541 --> 00:01:59,093
Charge to 200.

7
00:01:59,710 --> 00:02:01,011
Clear!

8
00:02:02,379 --> 00:02:03,780
Charge to 200 again.

9
00:02:15,134 --> 00:02:18,628
<i>He's still alive.</i>

10
00:02:18,628 --> 00:02:20,230
Prep the ECMO, now.

11
00:02:20,230 --> 00:02:23,323
Page the transport team and get CS down here.

12
00:02:23,323 --> 00:02:25,267
- All hands on deck, move.
- On it.

13
00:02:25,267 --> 00:02:27,670
- Right now.
- Yes, Doctor.

14
00:02:30,667 --> 00:02:32,847
Why are you giving up already? Do more!

15
00:02:32,847 --> 00:02:35,078
Do whatever you can!

16
00:02:35,712 --> 00:02:37,370
Show some respect for the dead.

17
00:02:37,370 --> 00:02:39,616
This doesn't concern you.

18
00:02:43,687 --> 00:02:45,701
Mom!

19
00:02:45,701 --> 00:02:47,924
Mom, are you okay?

20
00:02:55,632 --> 00:02:56,700
[Il Jun's Mom]

21
00:02:58,301 --> 00:03:00,096
[Il Jun's Dad]

22
00:03:02,233 --> 00:03:03,740
<i>The person you are trying to reach
is not answering...</i>

23
00:03:03,740 --> 00:03:06,109
You just won't stop, will you...

24
00:03:13,083 --> 00:03:14,517
Doctor.

25
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:18,888
Yeah, I need a minute alone.

26
00:03:35,534 --> 00:03:37,707
What the hell are you doing?

27
00:03:37,707 --> 00:03:38,806
Jae Seong.

28
00:03:38,806 --> 00:03:40,947
Did Jae Gyeong tell you to finish him off?

29
00:03:40,947 --> 00:03:43,746
What did you people do to my father?

30
00:03:44,581 --> 00:03:46,727
I think she injected him with sleeping pills.

31
00:03:46,727 --> 00:03:49,407
If I don't give him the antidote right now,
he's going to die.

32
00:03:49,407 --> 00:03:51,119
What are you talking about?

33
00:03:51,119 --> 00:03:53,046
Are you saying we can save him?

34
00:03:53,046 --> 00:03:55,491
I've got a faint heartbeat.

35
00:03:56,698 --> 00:03:59,796
We have to save him, no matter what.

36
00:04:03,567 --> 00:04:05,126
Are you sure?

37
00:04:05,126 --> 00:04:07,737
If you're messing with me about my father...

38
00:04:13,634 --> 00:04:15,044
Dad.

39
00:04:15,934 --> 00:04:17,183
Mr. Kang.

40
00:04:17,183 --> 00:04:18,715
Dad.

41
00:04:25,134 --> 00:04:26,988
He's breathing.

42
00:04:26,988 --> 00:04:28,991
Dad's breathing.

43
00:04:31,303 --> 00:04:33,904
I've got a pulse. We got him back.

44
00:04:33,904 --> 00:04:35,899
Dad.

45
00:04:35,899 --> 00:04:37,105
It's me.

46
00:04:37,105 --> 00:04:39,567
Jae Seong. I'm here.

47
00:04:39,567 --> 00:04:44,545
I knew you wouldn't let it end this way.

48
00:04:44,545 --> 00:04:47,877
No way you'd let
that bitch Jae Gyeong take you down.

49
00:04:49,980 --> 00:04:51,425
[Il Jun's Mom]

50
00:04:54,584 --> 00:04:56,160
[Il Jun's Mom]

51
00:04:58,855 --> 00:05:01,857
Go play along with your wife.

52
00:05:03,126 --> 00:05:06,062
Make sure she believes Dad is dead.
Not a word about this.

53
00:05:06,062 --> 00:05:08,631
He passed away a short while ago.

54
00:05:08,631 --> 00:05:10,600
What exactly is your plan?

55
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:15,805
It's time...

56
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:19,208
I stepped up as the eldest son.

57
00:05:22,912 --> 00:05:26,186
[Unclaimed Body]

58
00:05:36,712 --> 00:05:38,173
<i>Dad, aren't you sad?</i>

59
00:05:38,173 --> 00:05:40,797
<i>Grandpa just died.</i>

60
00:05:42,567 --> 00:05:43,901
<i>Congrats, honey.</i>

61
00:05:43,901 --> 00:05:46,670
<i>You got everything you wanted.</i>

62
00:05:46,670 --> 00:05:50,424
<i>I just want the truth about how he died.</i>

63
00:05:51,341 --> 00:05:52,942
<i>Then I'll be punished.</i>

64
00:05:54,452 --> 00:05:56,446
<i>I'm the one who should be glaring.</i>

65
00:05:56,446 --> 00:05:59,382
<i>Being linked to you
has been nothing but bad luck.</i>

66
00:06:00,801 --> 00:06:02,619
<i>I swore on Dad's grave.</i>

67
00:06:02,619 --> 00:06:05,455
<i>From now on, my only sister is you.</i>

68
00:06:05,455 --> 00:06:06,490
Dad.

69
00:06:06,490 --> 00:06:09,759
<i>And I owe you years of being a real brother.</i>

70
00:06:13,134 --> 00:06:14,630
Dad.

71
00:06:17,801 --> 00:06:19,135
Dad.

72
00:06:19,135 --> 00:06:20,804
Just hang in there a little longer.

73
00:06:20,804 --> 00:06:22,605
You're going to pull through.

74
00:06:29,567 --> 00:06:31,114
Not again...

75
00:06:31,114 --> 00:06:33,049
He's dead.

76
00:06:44,534 --> 00:06:46,028
Bang Geul.

77
00:06:47,068 --> 00:06:48,731
Bang Geul!

78
00:06:55,272 --> 00:06:57,340
We've got an injured person over here!

79
00:06:57,340 --> 00:06:59,009
Call an ambulance!

80
00:06:59,009 --> 00:07:01,111
Ambulance!

81
00:07:01,111 --> 00:07:03,446
You can stop running now.

82
00:07:04,934 --> 00:07:07,001
Bang Geul.

83
00:07:07,001 --> 00:07:10,420
Why are you being so loud?

84
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:13,075
You're giving me a splitting headache.

85
00:07:15,168 --> 00:07:16,726
Bang Geul.

86
00:07:43,967 --> 00:07:45,397
You're here.

87
00:07:45,397 --> 00:07:47,189
Is everyone okay?

88
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,794
What happened to your head?

89
00:07:51,794 --> 00:07:53,687
Shouldn't you go to the hospital?

90
00:07:53,687 --> 00:07:56,307
They said it's just a small cut. I'm fine.

91
00:07:56,307 --> 00:07:59,274
Honestly, I thought it was really bad.

92
00:07:59,274 --> 00:08:01,205
Isn't that right?

93
00:08:04,325 --> 00:08:07,168
A second ago you were running
with her in your arms

94
00:08:07,168 --> 00:08:09,101
like she was dying.

95
00:08:09,101 --> 00:08:11,907
Why are you standing there like a statue now?

96
00:08:11,907 --> 00:08:13,183
Go to the ER.

97
00:08:13,183 --> 00:08:14,818
Get a CT, an MRI.

98
00:08:14,818 --> 00:08:16,186
Don't come crying later when it hurts.

99
00:08:16,186 --> 00:08:18,121
Don't make a big deal out of it.

100
00:08:18,121 --> 00:08:20,126
Stop holding up busy people.

101
00:08:20,126 --> 00:08:22,034
Thank you.

102
00:08:22,034 --> 00:08:24,226
- Thank you so much.
- Thank you.

103
00:08:25,462 --> 00:08:26,567
Hey.

104
00:08:26,567 --> 00:08:28,634
Why would you let
Secretary Jo get his hands on that?

105
00:08:28,634 --> 00:08:31,052
You really want Choiseong to go under?

106
00:08:31,052 --> 00:08:33,202
That's what I'm saying.

107
00:08:33,834 --> 00:08:39,042
For God's sake, just tell me what you're up to.

108
00:08:39,042 --> 00:08:40,517
We need to have a chat, you and me.

109
00:08:40,517 --> 00:08:41,544
You want to talk to me?

110
00:08:41,544 --> 00:08:43,112
I've got something important
to talk to you about.

111
00:08:43,112 --> 00:08:46,120
But I need answers from him.

112
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:48,213
I should be in on this.

113
00:08:57,612 --> 00:08:59,181
Hey, Jun Hyeon.

114
00:09:01,631 --> 00:09:03,408
Should I march up to Jae Gyeong and tell her

115
00:09:03,408 --> 00:09:05,789
you're teaming up with Taeha to screw her over?

116
00:09:06,937 --> 00:09:08,440
Or maybe...

117
00:09:10,267 --> 00:09:12,175
I bring this to Chairman Na?

118
00:09:12,175 --> 00:09:14,176
Where did you get that?

119
00:09:15,233 --> 00:09:16,340
I stole it.

120
00:09:16,340 --> 00:09:17,714
Right out of Chairman Na's house.

121
00:09:17,714 --> 00:09:20,016
That guy Na Byeong Mo is no joke.

122
00:09:20,016 --> 00:09:22,652
What were you thinking?

123
00:09:23,419 --> 00:09:24,520
<i>Open your eyes!</i>

124
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:25,700
<i>Wake up. Bang Geul!</i>

125
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:27,189
<i>Can't you hear Dad?</i>

126
00:09:29,290 --> 00:09:31,529
Why do you care so much?

127
00:09:31,529 --> 00:09:32,262
What?

128
00:09:32,262 --> 00:09:34,498
You're worried about me.

129
00:09:34,498 --> 00:09:37,032
Everything you've been doing
was to keep me safe.

130
00:09:39,102 --> 00:09:41,137
She's my sister. He was my dad.

131
00:09:41,137 --> 00:09:42,331
The revenge is mine to take.

132
00:09:42,331 --> 00:09:44,211
Who are you to be jumping in?

133
00:09:44,211 --> 00:09:45,910
Why are you telling me to stay out of it?

134
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,077
Who do you think you are?

135
00:09:47,077 --> 00:09:48,344
Yes,

136
00:09:48,344 --> 00:09:52,582
I'm losing sleep over you,
over your mom getting dragged into this.

137
00:09:52,582 --> 00:09:54,233
I'm worried sick

138
00:09:54,233 --> 00:09:57,319
you'll play avenger
and get caught by those bastards.

139
00:09:59,001 --> 00:10:00,489
"Those bastards"?

140
00:10:02,125 --> 00:10:05,595
Chairman Na was involved in killing my dad?

141
00:10:05,595 --> 00:10:08,665
Don't tell me he was Jae Gyeong's accomplice.

142
00:10:08,665 --> 00:10:10,199
Hwang Jun Hyeon!

143
00:10:13,233 --> 00:10:15,638
I've been digging
into the security guard's phone

144
00:10:15,638 --> 00:10:17,506
trying to recover the hospital CCTV.

145
00:10:19,271 --> 00:10:24,219
They framed Jae Gyeong to grab Choiseong.

146
00:10:25,604 --> 00:10:27,717
Na Eun Se's the one who killed him.

147
00:10:34,734 --> 00:10:36,225
You sure?

148
00:10:44,110 --> 00:10:45,654
So my dad...

149
00:10:46,636 --> 00:10:51,741
was just a pawn the whole time?

150
00:10:59,034 --> 00:11:01,350
I'm really grateful for everything you've done.

151
00:11:02,233 --> 00:11:03,886
But step back.

152
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:06,455
This is my fight.

153
00:11:07,177 --> 00:11:08,658
They've killed people.

154
00:11:08,658 --> 00:11:11,237
You can't go after them by yourself!

155
00:11:11,237 --> 00:11:13,262
My heart just breaks for Dad.

156
00:11:14,127 --> 00:11:16,967
I need to show Dad he wasn't forgotten.

157
00:11:16,967 --> 00:11:21,638
I want him to know his life...

158
00:11:21,638 --> 00:11:23,405
wasn't some lonely ending.

159
00:11:37,734 --> 00:11:39,255
Don't...

160
00:11:41,634 --> 00:11:45,928
let this make you ugly, Bang Geul.

161
00:11:49,299 --> 00:11:54,570
Once your hands are dirty, once you turn cold,
revenge ends up...

162
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,741
wrecking you.

163
00:12:00,467 --> 00:12:03,146
I don't want that for you.

164
00:12:03,146 --> 00:12:05,083
I'll handle the dirty work.

165
00:12:09,034 --> 00:12:11,687
I said this is my fight.

166
00:12:11,687 --> 00:12:14,924
- Why would you...
- Because your dad wouldn't want it.

167
00:12:18,337 --> 00:12:21,931
No dad in the world
wants his daughter to go down

168
00:12:24,867 --> 00:12:26,836
because of him.

169
00:12:39,801 --> 00:12:42,037
Come clean.

170
00:12:42,037 --> 00:12:44,480
You're hiding a daughter, aren't you?

171
00:12:47,868 --> 00:12:50,559
I'm letting you in.

172
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:54,797
From now on, we do this together.

173
00:12:56,208 --> 00:12:57,600
Okay.

174
00:13:00,736 --> 00:13:03,906
[Chairman Na Byeong Mo]

175
00:13:03,906 --> 00:13:07,076
First, let's take down Secretary Jo.

176
00:13:19,950 --> 00:13:25,027
You want to... explain what happened today?

177
00:13:31,267 --> 00:13:33,770
Before that, you should get a new secretary.

178
00:13:33,770 --> 00:13:36,907
How long are you going
to keep this thug by your side?

179
00:13:36,907 --> 00:13:39,675
You're a chairman of a major conglomerate now.

180
00:13:40,758 --> 00:13:44,200
Thanks to him,
I look like I can't even finish off Bang Geul.

181
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,681
But...

182
00:13:46,849 --> 00:13:50,053
He nearly ruined
the whole thing just to take credit.

183
00:13:50,053 --> 00:13:53,880
Plenty of smart guys out there.
Why waste time on this clown?

184
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:54,991
Hwang Jun Hyeon.

185
00:13:54,991 --> 00:13:56,492
Enough.

186
00:13:58,640 --> 00:14:01,849
Get this to Taeha Energy.
Have them check the tech.

187
00:14:01,849 --> 00:14:04,101
Results will tell us.

188
00:14:04,101 --> 00:14:08,070
Brains or fists. We'll see which I need.

189
00:14:16,833 --> 00:14:18,913
What if Jae Gyeong starts asking questions?

190
00:14:18,913 --> 00:14:20,249
There was an incident.

191
00:14:20,249 --> 00:14:24,153
She's aware her sister's been making noise.
I'll blame her for it.

192
00:14:25,293 --> 00:14:27,273
She makes a decent shield.

193
00:14:27,273 --> 00:14:30,660
She lost the very tech she was about to sell.

194
00:14:30,660 --> 00:14:33,789
Her position is shaky.

195
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,504
[Lee Sang Jae]
<i>Forensics complete.</i>

196
00:14:41,504 --> 00:14:44,573
<i>Original CCTV recovered.</i>

197
00:14:46,954 --> 00:14:49,244
This is going to be one to watch.

198
00:14:50,934 --> 00:14:52,948
Look forward to it, Chairman.

199
00:15:08,767 --> 00:15:11,533
What is she doing here this late?

200
00:15:14,371 --> 00:15:19,142
<i>They framed Jae Gyeong to grab Choiseong.</i>

201
00:15:19,142 --> 00:15:21,275
<i>Na Eun Se's the one who killed him.</i>

202
00:15:33,634 --> 00:15:35,257
Lost your mind?

203
00:15:35,257 --> 00:15:37,026
You asking for it?

204
00:15:45,701 --> 00:15:47,068
You okay?

205
00:15:47,068 --> 00:15:48,267
Have you lost your mind?

206
00:15:48,267 --> 00:15:49,673
She's the crazy one.

207
00:15:49,673 --> 00:15:51,073
Hey!

208
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,810
What's with the look?

209
00:15:53,810 --> 00:15:55,702
Wishing you'd died?

210
00:15:55,702 --> 00:15:57,922
Take it up with Jae Gyeong.

211
00:15:57,922 --> 00:16:00,549
Don't come crying to me.

212
00:16:00,549 --> 00:16:02,451
You feel untouchable now?

213
00:16:04,388 --> 00:16:06,102
Like the world is yours?

214
00:16:06,102 --> 00:16:07,556
Bang Geul.

215
00:16:10,233 --> 00:16:12,462
I outrank you in this family.

216
00:16:12,462 --> 00:16:14,830
Watch your mouth.

217
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:20,212
You want to see me push it? I'll show you.

218
00:16:20,212 --> 00:16:21,852
Stay tuned.

219
00:16:23,034 --> 00:16:24,540
Go ahead.

220
00:16:25,432 --> 00:16:28,210
Who are you to scare me?

221
00:16:30,714 --> 00:16:32,982
That's enough. Go inside.

222
00:16:32,982 --> 00:16:34,801
Get off me.

223
00:16:34,801 --> 00:16:36,667
Blood really is thicker than water, huh?

224
00:16:36,667 --> 00:16:39,034
Seriously...

225
00:16:39,034 --> 00:16:43,659
I'm done with the Kangs.

226
00:16:57,741 --> 00:17:00,409
Spitting image of her father. More and more.

227
00:17:00,409 --> 00:17:01,809
Right?

228
00:17:03,233 --> 00:17:05,975
Hey, did that shake you up?

229
00:17:05,975 --> 00:17:08,085
Your head's hurt, right? Is that what it is?

230
00:17:08,085 --> 00:17:10,853
- Forget it, let's get you to a hospital.
- Jae Seong.

231
00:17:18,559 --> 00:17:23,765
It was Na Eun Se... Taeha was behind it...

232
00:17:47,991 --> 00:17:50,200
<i>Don't trust that girl.</i>

233
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:55,831
<i>Chairman Na never makes a losing trade,
so why hand her to someone like you?</i>

234
00:17:55,831 --> 00:18:00,536
<i>Come on, I said don't worry about Eun Se.</i>

235
00:18:03,734 --> 00:18:05,541
Stupid bastard.

236
00:18:06,634 --> 00:18:08,577
Moron.

237
00:18:12,034 --> 00:18:13,982
This is all your fault.

238
00:18:17,167 --> 00:18:20,989
None of this would've happened without you.

239
00:18:23,068 --> 00:18:25,327
You did this.

240
00:18:44,034 --> 00:18:45,614
Mom!

241
00:18:45,614 --> 00:18:48,513
Let go! I'm bringing him home right now.

242
00:18:48,513 --> 00:18:50,786
Mom, just calm down first.

243
00:18:50,786 --> 00:18:54,089
Can you imagine what he's going through?

244
00:18:54,853 --> 00:18:59,195
What kind of life will Yi Jun have
under that woman?

245
00:18:59,195 --> 00:19:00,797
Are they even human?

246
00:19:00,797 --> 00:19:05,126
How could they do this to your dad?

247
00:19:05,126 --> 00:19:06,853
I know, Mom.

248
00:19:06,853 --> 00:19:13,134
I want to kill them right now,
but I'm holding back for Dad.

249
00:19:13,134 --> 00:19:16,400
I'm going to make
those scumbags tear each other apart.

250
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:18,247
We are not sinking to their level.

251
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:21,701
Mom.

252
00:19:21,701 --> 00:19:23,552
How could they...

253
00:19:31,967 --> 00:19:34,196
We're all set, Chairman.

254
00:19:37,739 --> 00:19:41,267
I told you to lay low
until you take over as president of Trading.

255
00:19:41,267 --> 00:19:44,508
I have to file for divorce anyway
because of Yi Jun.

256
00:19:44,508 --> 00:19:48,345
Since it's happening,
I refuse to spend another day in that house.

257
00:19:48,345 --> 00:19:50,266
It's not a good look.

258
00:19:50,266 --> 00:19:52,758
Why does that matter?

259
00:19:52,758 --> 00:19:55,183
We have Jae Gyeong right where we want her.

260
00:19:59,288 --> 00:20:00,682
[Managing Director Kwon]

261
00:20:01,367 --> 00:20:02,991
Yes, MD Kwon.

262
00:20:06,834 --> 00:20:09,097
Wait, what are you talking about?

263
00:20:11,300 --> 00:20:12,971
[Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong]

264
00:20:15,101 --> 00:20:16,772
You're firing me?

265
00:20:17,467 --> 00:20:18,770
On whose authority?

266
00:20:18,770 --> 00:20:22,250
Hiring and firing is a perk
of being the chairman.

267
00:20:22,250 --> 00:20:26,482
You think your position is safe
if you kick me out?

268
00:20:26,482 --> 00:20:28,250
I'm shaking.

269
00:20:28,950 --> 00:20:32,487
Are you really going to take me down?

270
00:20:37,267 --> 00:20:39,027
You're going to regret this.

271
00:20:50,662 --> 00:20:52,582
Aren't you pushing her a little too hard?

272
00:20:52,582 --> 00:20:55,245
She needs to be provoked to show her hand.

273
00:20:55,245 --> 00:20:57,510
I made that call because I trust you.

274
00:20:59,915 --> 00:21:01,901
You said you found
the hospital security footage.

275
00:21:01,901 --> 00:21:06,121
I searched the dead security guard's house
and found his phone.

276
00:21:09,267 --> 00:21:11,326
Here's the recovered footage.

277
00:21:16,367 --> 00:21:20,170
I wonder just how far Eun Se is willing to go.

278
00:21:20,170 --> 00:21:22,600
Are you just going to let her
get away with this?

279
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:24,267
Let's leak the security footage
and the recording

280
00:21:24,267 --> 00:21:25,941
and destroy Choiseong, Dad.

281
00:21:25,941 --> 00:21:28,863
<i>Don't do anything rash and just wait.</i>

282
00:21:28,863 --> 00:21:31,146
How much longer!

283
00:21:39,421 --> 00:21:40,813
[CEO Jeong Hak Hui, Hayoung Daily]

284
00:21:45,001 --> 00:21:49,666
CEO Jeong, go ahead and publish that tip.

285
00:21:49,666 --> 00:21:51,934
[Late Chairman Kang's Death: Footage Leaked]

286
00:21:51,934 --> 00:21:53,035
[Shocking Footage of Chairman Kang's Death]

287
00:21:53,035 --> 00:21:54,600
[The Truth Behind Chairman Kang's Death]

288
00:21:54,600 --> 00:21:57,534
<i>At first,
she tried to inject the sleeping pills</i>

289
00:21:57,534 --> 00:22:00,515
<i>she got from her husband
so Dad wouldn't wake up.</i>

290
00:22:00,515 --> 00:22:06,115
<i>But when he suddenly opened his eyes,
she just smothered him with a pillow.</i>

291
00:22:06,115 --> 00:22:08,351
<i>Your husband is an accomplice, too.</i>

292
00:22:08,351 --> 00:22:10,919
<i>Do you really want to argue
over whose crime is worse?</i>

293
00:22:10,919 --> 00:22:12,021
[If he's an accomplice, they did it together]

294
00:22:12,021 --> 00:22:13,989
[Life in prison is too good for them]

295
00:22:13,989 --> 00:22:15,157
[Views]

296
00:22:15,157 --> 00:22:16,525
[The released transcript may be
the only key evidence revealing the crime]

297
00:22:16,525 --> 00:22:22,468
[Suspicious Death: Who Was the Last Visitor?]

298
00:22:23,834 --> 00:22:27,135
I told her to wait,
but she still went and pulled this stunt?

299
00:22:33,333 --> 00:22:34,534
Chairman,

300
00:22:34,534 --> 00:22:37,938
there's an issue with the hydrogen tech files
we took from Choiseong.

301
00:22:37,938 --> 00:22:39,481
We checked them several times,

302
00:22:39,481 --> 00:22:42,751
but they're an older version
than what we already had.

303
00:22:46,333 --> 00:22:48,523
<i>This is going to be one to watch.</i>

304
00:22:49,299 --> 00:22:51,486
<i>Look forward to it, Chairman.</i>

305
00:22:51,486 --> 00:22:54,095
Hwang Jun Hyeon, that bastard.

306
00:23:06,333 --> 00:23:10,814
[Choiseong Press Briefing]
I deeply apologize for the shock

307
00:23:10,814 --> 00:23:13,962
and disappointment many of you must have felt.

308
00:23:15,804 --> 00:23:18,200
After much agonizing,

309
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:21,389
I am standing here today because I decided

310
00:23:22,891 --> 00:23:25,060
I can no longer hide the truth.

311
00:23:26,530 --> 00:23:30,966
The truth is, I am being blackmailed

312
00:23:33,704 --> 00:23:36,438
over my father's death.

313
00:23:38,567 --> 00:23:40,875
Is it true you visited
his hospital room that day?

314
00:23:40,875 --> 00:23:43,011
Are you also denying
the contents of the recording?

315
00:23:43,011 --> 00:23:46,034
We suspect the person
demanding a huge sum of money

316
00:23:46,034 --> 00:23:48,817
with the fabricated recording and footage

317
00:23:48,817 --> 00:23:53,467
is the same individual

318
00:23:53,467 --> 00:23:57,259
who broke
into the Daesan Hydrogen Complex recently

319
00:23:58,058 --> 00:24:00,499
and leaked our core hydrogen tech.

320
00:24:00,499 --> 00:24:02,459
Have you identified a suspect?

321
00:24:02,459 --> 00:24:06,535
We handed their identity over to the police
along with the security footage as evidence.

322
00:24:06,535 --> 00:24:09,104
We also believe
the real culprit who killed my father

323
00:24:09,104 --> 00:24:11,119
is part of the same group.

324
00:24:11,119 --> 00:24:14,576
Are you saying
the late Chairman Kang Yong Ho was murdered?

325
00:24:17,801 --> 00:24:20,782
We've secured evidence
pointing to the real culprit.

326
00:24:28,056 --> 00:24:29,170
[Choiseong Press Briefing]

327
00:24:29,967 --> 00:24:31,901
What is that?

328
00:24:31,901 --> 00:24:33,762
Isn't that Chairman Kang?

329
00:24:43,934 --> 00:24:48,600
Did the culprit dress up as you
to kill your father?

330
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:49,789
Do you also have the original footage?

331
00:24:49,789 --> 00:24:51,587
You used the word "group."

332
00:24:51,587 --> 00:24:53,200
Are you saying they didn't act alone?

333
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:54,600
Can you identify them?

334
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:56,034
Is it someone from inside Choiseong?

335
00:24:56,034 --> 00:24:58,134
Why are you just now releasing the footage?

336
00:24:58,134 --> 00:24:59,688
I ask that...

337
00:25:03,500 --> 00:25:05,994
you stop exploiting...

338
00:25:06,867 --> 00:25:09,567
my father's death...

339
00:25:09,567 --> 00:25:15,203
so he can... finally rest in peace.

340
00:25:24,233 --> 00:25:26,982
Her acting is seriously giving me the creeps.

341
00:25:33,824 --> 00:25:38,526
She's just using my dad
right up to the very end.

342
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:52,074
Public opinion has completely flipped.

343
00:25:52,074 --> 00:25:54,411
There are wild guesses flying around
about the real culprit.

344
00:25:54,411 --> 00:25:57,946
Since your daughter is also implicated
in the recording,

345
00:25:57,946 --> 00:26:00,982
the focus might shift to Taeha
if we're not careful.

346
00:26:02,701 --> 00:26:04,419
What do we do, Dad?

347
00:26:04,419 --> 00:26:08,556
When you swing a sword recklessly,
you're bound to cut yourself.

348
00:26:10,367 --> 00:26:13,028
How does Jae Gyeong have the original footage?

349
00:26:13,028 --> 00:26:14,752
You said you took care of everything.

350
00:26:14,752 --> 00:26:17,134
You blaming your own father now?

351
00:26:17,134 --> 00:26:21,134
You forced me in there
because you got sick of waiting around

352
00:26:21,134 --> 00:26:23,505
for somebody else to bring you Choiseong.

353
00:26:24,351 --> 00:26:26,451
You wanted me to be the one to finish him off.

354
00:26:26,451 --> 00:26:27,477
So?

355
00:26:27,477 --> 00:26:32,347
Nobody was happier than you
when Chairman Kang died,

356
00:26:35,697 --> 00:26:40,255
so I don't deserve any of this.

357
00:26:42,101 --> 00:26:44,534
- Hey, stop them!
- Who are you people?

358
00:26:44,534 --> 00:26:46,161
Who are you people?

359
00:26:46,161 --> 00:26:47,218
Jo Taek Sang,

360
00:26:47,218 --> 00:26:49,767
you're under arrest for trespassing
and industrial espionage.

361
00:26:49,767 --> 00:26:51,278
You have the right to an attorney.

362
00:26:51,278 --> 00:26:55,400
You have the right to remain silent,
and anything you say can be used against you.

363
00:26:55,400 --> 00:26:59,634
Heads up.
You, your chairman, and the executives

364
00:26:59,634 --> 00:27:02,644
could all be brought in over that stolen tech.

365
00:27:06,834 --> 00:27:08,883
Dad.

366
00:27:12,788 --> 00:27:15,595
[Kang Jae Gyeong]

367
00:27:33,873 --> 00:27:35,410
This way.

368
00:27:39,967 --> 00:27:41,783
Brains always win, don't they?

369
00:27:42,634 --> 00:27:45,455
Looks like you need a new secretary.

370
00:27:45,455 --> 00:27:48,890
Good luck finding talent like mine.

371
00:27:49,526 --> 00:27:52,761
Remember that security guard you killed?

372
00:27:52,761 --> 00:27:55,198
Mr. Hwang found his phone.

373
00:27:55,198 --> 00:27:57,467
Found some pretty interesting stuff on it.

374
00:27:57,467 --> 00:28:00,935
Should've killed that bastard too.

375
00:28:03,959 --> 00:28:07,456
Thanks to you, I had the best laugh in ages.

376
00:28:08,134 --> 00:28:10,347
Really something, aren't you?

377
00:28:10,347 --> 00:28:14,383
You made your daughter do the killing.

378
00:28:14,383 --> 00:28:17,452
I'm actually starting to feel bad for her.

379
00:28:18,434 --> 00:28:22,834
By the way, once people find out...

380
00:28:22,834 --> 00:28:28,844
you murdered your in-law for Choiseong,
Taeha's done, right?

381
00:28:31,972 --> 00:28:34,202
I've got a soft heart.

382
00:28:35,371 --> 00:28:38,141
Hand over Taeha Energy.

383
00:28:38,141 --> 00:28:40,711
You nearly framed me
as the beast who murdered Dad.

384
00:28:40,711 --> 00:28:44,467
That much is the bare minimum
if you want my help.

385
00:28:44,467 --> 00:28:45,767
And...

386
00:28:45,767 --> 00:28:48,950
The money for the buyout?

387
00:28:48,950 --> 00:28:51,319
That's on you, right?

388
00:28:53,867 --> 00:28:58,593
You've got a stash tucked away in Singapore.

389
00:29:16,422 --> 00:29:20,034
Mr. Hwang dug that up too.

390
00:29:20,034 --> 00:29:22,417
He scares even me sometimes.

391
00:29:26,001 --> 00:29:28,056
A lot to think about, isn't it?

392
00:29:29,024 --> 00:29:32,861
Cutting your daughter loose
won't make this go away.

393
00:29:32,861 --> 00:29:35,163
- Watch your mouth.
- Keep your voice down.

394
00:29:35,163 --> 00:29:36,731
Dad.

395
00:29:43,901 --> 00:29:49,851
I'll think about it
if you bury Kang Yong Ho's death for good.

396
00:29:51,990 --> 00:29:54,682
The living have to keep living.

397
00:29:55,824 --> 00:30:01,812
I'm not cruel enough
to cut off your people's livelihood.

398
00:30:16,767 --> 00:30:20,141
How did you find out about this?

399
00:30:20,141 --> 00:30:24,881
You asked Chairman Kang
about overseas tax havens before, didn't you?

400
00:30:24,881 --> 00:30:27,616
Even though he called you pathetic

401
00:30:27,616 --> 00:30:31,887
for cheaply copying
everything a chaebol chairman does.

402
00:30:31,887 --> 00:30:33,888
How do you know that?

403
00:30:33,888 --> 00:30:38,026
Since you were family,
he couldn't just ignore you.

404
00:30:39,596 --> 00:30:43,131
He showed you how,
but kept copies of all the documents.

405
00:30:43,131 --> 00:30:45,066
[Taeha Group Chairman Na Byeong Mo's
Slush Fund Records]

406
00:30:45,066 --> 00:30:47,435
Of course, even Chairman Kang never thought

407
00:30:47,435 --> 00:30:50,138
this card would be used
in a situation like this.

408
00:30:50,138 --> 00:30:52,173
Chairman Kang told you?

409
00:30:52,173 --> 00:30:53,273
Why?

410
00:30:53,273 --> 00:30:54,760
Who exactly are you?

411
00:30:54,760 --> 00:30:56,177
Good question.

412
00:30:57,667 --> 00:30:59,714
Who do you think I am?

413
00:31:01,885 --> 00:31:06,688
Please get ready
for Singapore as soon as possible.

414
00:31:14,996 --> 00:31:18,500
[Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong]

415
00:31:22,141 --> 00:31:27,075
Thanks to you,
I kept my seat and got Taeha Energy.

416
00:31:28,076 --> 00:31:32,516
I pulled off what my father couldn't.

417
00:31:32,516 --> 00:31:35,598
What would I ever do without you?

418
00:31:38,434 --> 00:31:42,690
<i>Should we just swallow Taeha whole?</i>

419
00:31:43,894 --> 00:31:45,860
Not on my watch.

420
00:31:52,195 --> 00:31:54,134
Where have you been this late?

421
00:31:54,134 --> 00:31:57,774
Just... went for a walk.

422
00:31:57,774 --> 00:31:59,675
It's dangerous out there...

423
00:32:04,619 --> 00:32:06,700
It'll be over soon.

424
00:32:07,787 --> 00:32:10,251
Kang Jae Gyeong and Taeha.

425
00:32:13,154 --> 00:32:14,554
Well...

426
00:32:15,500 --> 00:32:17,434
About Seok Do...

427
00:32:17,434 --> 00:32:18,826
What?

428
00:32:21,884 --> 00:32:23,564
Never mind.

429
00:32:24,534 --> 00:32:26,768
You're going on a business trip tomorrow?

430
00:32:42,113 --> 00:32:43,901
You came alone?

431
00:32:43,901 --> 00:32:45,253
You've got some nerve.

432
00:32:45,253 --> 00:32:49,657
She said she won't let it slide
if I get a single scratch.

433
00:32:51,634 --> 00:32:54,695
Do whatever you want
if you want to make the 9 o'clock news.

434
00:32:56,034 --> 00:32:57,365
Oh, I'm terrified.

435
00:32:57,365 --> 00:32:58,568
Economy?

436
00:32:58,568 --> 00:33:01,480
You should spend a little money
for an important trip like this.

437
00:33:01,480 --> 00:33:02,839
I'm in first class.

438
00:33:02,839 --> 00:33:04,264
First.

439
00:33:06,474 --> 00:33:08,342
That little...

440
00:33:12,434 --> 00:33:15,420
Yes, Chairman, I'm boarding now.

441
00:33:15,420 --> 00:33:17,940
Did you get the money launderers?

442
00:33:17,940 --> 00:33:20,321
<i>The guys who helped you set up Siren.</i>

443
00:33:20,321 --> 00:33:23,057
I arranged for you to meet them in Singapore.

444
00:33:24,383 --> 00:33:25,600
What about the shell company

445
00:33:25,600 --> 00:33:28,104
to use as a cushion
for Na Byeong Mo's money laundering?

446
00:33:28,104 --> 00:33:31,032
I have an expert for that, so don't worry.

447
00:33:31,032 --> 00:33:32,602
<i>I'm not worried.</i>

448
00:33:32,602 --> 00:33:34,201
<i>Keep up the good work.</i>

449
00:33:36,267 --> 00:33:38,005
Careful there.

450
00:33:39,767 --> 00:33:41,275
Thank you.

451
00:33:46,734 --> 00:33:50,585
Why is she dressed like that again?

452
00:33:53,367 --> 00:33:55,389
Everyone's staring.

453
00:33:56,791 --> 00:33:58,454
[Taeha Energy Business and Operations Analysis]

454
00:34:06,534 --> 00:34:10,348
Let's wrap up the Taeha Energy M&amp;A plan
before Team Leader Hwang gets back.

455
00:34:10,348 --> 00:34:12,206
- Yes, Chairman.
- Yes, Chairman.

456
00:34:13,908 --> 00:34:15,309
What about my husband?

457
00:34:16,333 --> 00:34:18,279
What's he been up to lately?

458
00:34:35,932 --> 00:34:41,202
You always blew me off saying you were busy,
but you're sure playing a lot of golf.

459
00:34:42,534 --> 00:34:45,940
I haven't played in a while,
so my body feels stiff.

460
00:34:46,674 --> 00:34:48,545
Plus, you've been busy.

461
00:34:50,467 --> 00:34:52,816
You've changed a bit.

462
00:34:52,816 --> 00:34:54,620
Your whole vibe, too.

463
00:34:55,834 --> 00:34:57,903
We went through a lot.

464
00:34:57,903 --> 00:35:00,054
Anyone would change after that.

465
00:35:10,767 --> 00:35:14,902
Do you like... the new car?

466
00:35:37,559 --> 00:35:39,760
[Therapeutic Strategies
for Recovery in Hypoxic Brain Injury]

467
00:35:51,736 --> 00:35:55,242
Are you doing volunteer work... out of guilt?

468
00:35:55,242 --> 00:35:56,867
Or...

469
00:35:56,867 --> 00:35:59,447
are you trying to resurrect my cremated father?

470
00:36:14,333 --> 00:36:17,101
What would people say
if a guy who only saw patients

471
00:36:17,101 --> 00:36:19,069
suddenly jumped into corporate work?

472
00:36:19,069 --> 00:36:21,798
You want them calling me your nepotism hire?

473
00:36:21,798 --> 00:36:24,523
I don't want to be your puppet
in Chemicals or Trading.

474
00:36:24,523 --> 00:36:27,917
I'm thinking of starting
a medical business division for neurology.

475
00:36:27,917 --> 00:36:31,746
Treating your father
got me interested in coma cases.

476
00:36:36,517 --> 00:36:41,255
You quit the hospital,
yet you took syringes and coma meds with you.

477
00:36:42,277 --> 00:36:46,978
I just thought...
you were up to something shady.

478
00:36:46,978 --> 00:36:48,462
Jae Gyeong.

479
00:36:50,140 --> 00:36:51,666
Are you scared?

480
00:36:52,448 --> 00:36:54,702
Scared that I'll leave you, too?

481
00:36:56,500 --> 00:36:58,408
Leave?

482
00:36:58,408 --> 00:37:00,548
I was the one who threw them away.

483
00:37:00,548 --> 00:37:05,267
I ended that toxic relationship
they called family.

484
00:37:05,267 --> 00:37:08,149
I only need you and Il Jun.

485
00:37:11,588 --> 00:37:15,489
I'll tell them to push forward
with the medical division.

486
00:37:17,168 --> 00:37:19,293
I'm the chairman of Choiseong.

487
00:37:20,043 --> 00:37:22,330
You have nothing to be ashamed of.

488
00:37:31,168 --> 00:37:33,808
- To the office.
- Yes, ma'am.

489
00:37:34,542 --> 00:37:36,743
I have a lot of TF team work.

490
00:37:36,743 --> 00:37:38,433
You're heading home, right?

491
00:38:18,755 --> 00:38:22,456
Sir, you absolutely cannot lose that car.

492
00:38:51,735 --> 00:38:53,387
Mrs. Jo.

493
00:38:58,795 --> 00:39:01,362
Hold on! Please listen to me first!

494
00:39:05,001 --> 00:39:06,534
Wait!

495
00:39:14,267 --> 00:39:16,410
How did you find this place?

496
00:39:40,037 --> 00:39:45,964
You've been doing this... behind my back?

497
00:39:46,774 --> 00:39:48,512
I'm sorry.

498
00:39:48,512 --> 00:39:50,400
I was terrified...

499
00:39:50,400 --> 00:39:54,751
he might take a turn for the worse
and hurt you even more.

500
00:39:54,751 --> 00:39:59,854
I was just too scared... to tell you.

501
00:39:59,854 --> 00:40:01,755
I have no excuses.

502
00:40:08,632 --> 00:40:10,764
Thank you, Jae Seong.

503
00:40:14,300 --> 00:40:18,305
Thank you... for saving him.

504
00:40:20,679 --> 00:40:23,789
Thank you for letting me see him again.

505
00:40:27,851 --> 00:40:30,420
I'm so grateful.

506
00:40:30,420 --> 00:40:32,025
I'll make sure...

507
00:40:32,634 --> 00:40:37,258
he wakes up, Mother.

508
00:40:46,334 --> 00:40:49,593
Is he really handing that slush fund
over to Kang Jae Gyeong?

509
00:40:49,593 --> 00:40:51,305
Not a chance.

510
00:40:52,192 --> 00:40:54,478
This is Na Byeong Mo's slush fund file.

511
00:40:54,478 --> 00:40:58,749
It has everything
from his Singapore accounts to his proxies.

512
00:40:58,749 --> 00:41:02,667
Jun Hyeon left it for us
to hand over to the police.

513
00:41:02,667 --> 00:41:06,667
Then why did they take Na Eun Se
all the way to Singapore?

514
00:41:06,667 --> 00:41:08,959
Bang Geul said it herself.

515
00:41:08,959 --> 00:41:10,791
"Manager,

516
00:41:10,791 --> 00:41:12,901
how solid do you think
a father-daughter bond is

517
00:41:12,901 --> 00:41:14,938
when they've committed murder?"

518
00:41:14,938 --> 00:41:18,201
Na Byeong Mo won't even consider
saving his daughter.

519
00:41:18,201 --> 00:41:20,479
He's only worried about the group taking a hit.

520
00:41:20,479 --> 00:41:22,005
Bingo.

521
00:41:22,005 --> 00:41:23,871
She said that's what they're counting on.

522
00:41:23,871 --> 00:41:26,658
What are you two doing? Come on out.

523
00:41:26,658 --> 00:41:29,012
- Coming.
- Yes, ma'am.

524
00:41:29,012 --> 00:41:30,447
Right.

525
00:41:34,568 --> 00:41:37,552
We'll keep you safe
until your grandson gets back.

526
00:41:37,552 --> 00:41:39,956
Just think of us as your two new sons.

527
00:41:39,956 --> 00:41:41,556
Makes you feel safe, right?

528
00:41:42,259 --> 00:41:43,758
I cooked up some chicken.

529
00:41:43,758 --> 00:41:45,128
Have a seat.

530
00:41:45,128 --> 00:41:47,086
Oh, really?

531
00:41:47,086 --> 00:41:48,095
Oh...

532
00:41:48,095 --> 00:41:51,899
I was actually just thinking
something smelled amazing.

533
00:41:52,709 --> 00:41:55,336
We're the ones
supposed to be taking care of you.

534
00:41:55,336 --> 00:41:58,706
I heard you help Jun Hyeon out a lot.

535
00:41:58,706 --> 00:42:01,776
The girl next door told me
you're his best friends.

536
00:42:01,776 --> 00:42:03,077
- Yes, ma'am.
- Yes, ma'am.

537
00:42:03,077 --> 00:42:04,178
You boys drink, right?

538
00:42:04,178 --> 00:42:06,930
- Thank you for the drinks.
- Stay seated.

539
00:42:06,930 --> 00:42:09,389
- I'll whip this up quickly.
- Sounds good.

540
00:42:09,389 --> 00:42:13,120
- It'll be right out.
- Looks like we're the ones being treated here.

541
00:42:15,289 --> 00:42:16,339
Are you crying again?

542
00:42:16,339 --> 00:42:18,575
Must be male menopause.

543
00:42:19,333 --> 00:42:22,173
Just wait till Jun Hyeon gets back.

544
00:42:22,173 --> 00:42:23,831
I'm going to treat him so well.

545
00:42:23,831 --> 00:42:25,466
Come on.

546
00:42:26,434 --> 00:42:28,205
Have a seat.

547
00:42:28,205 --> 00:42:32,573
[Singapore]

548
00:42:32,573 --> 00:42:35,946
Write Chairman Na's Singapore account here.

549
00:42:35,946 --> 00:42:39,146
Take seven percent.
Send the rest to this foundation account.

550
00:42:44,701 --> 00:42:46,834
A seven percent fee?

551
00:42:46,834 --> 00:42:48,901
So after taking a 35 billion won cut,

552
00:42:48,901 --> 00:42:53,360
Jae Gyeong is just pocketing
over 450 billion won.

553
00:42:55,667 --> 00:42:57,464
Just sign it.

554
00:42:58,566 --> 00:42:59,637
[JH Soccer Club]

555
00:42:59,637 --> 00:43:01,600
JH?

556
00:43:01,600 --> 00:43:03,837
As in Hwang Jun Hyeon's JH?

557
00:43:05,300 --> 00:43:09,014
You slapped this together for laundering,
then you'll shut it down. Right?

558
00:43:09,014 --> 00:43:11,901
An expert put a lot of thought into this.

559
00:43:11,901 --> 00:43:13,183
Who knows?

560
00:43:13,183 --> 00:43:15,283
It might actually become
a prestigious soccer foundation.

561
00:43:15,283 --> 00:43:17,826
Order some champagne.

562
00:43:17,826 --> 00:43:20,190
We have way too much time before our flight.

563
00:43:20,190 --> 00:43:22,272
Let me walk you out.

564
00:43:23,101 --> 00:43:25,125
Excuse me.

565
00:43:29,400 --> 00:43:33,934
You guys...
need to earn your plane tickets, right?

566
00:43:41,712 --> 00:43:43,589
[Kang Bang Geul]
<i>Let's begin.</i>

567
00:43:47,481 --> 00:43:48,590
[CEO Jeong, Hayoung Daily]

568
00:43:53,034 --> 00:43:55,531
It's me, Kang Jae Seong.

569
00:44:15,545 --> 00:44:18,267
Are you sure about this? Doing this to me?

570
00:44:18,267 --> 00:44:20,890
Stop acting up
just because you trust Jae Gyeong.

571
00:44:20,890 --> 00:44:23,617
Guys like you are disposable
and a dime a dozen.

572
00:44:24,390 --> 00:44:26,587
Who says I trust Kang Jae Gyeong?

573
00:44:37,134 --> 00:44:39,803
The Daesan Hydrogen Complex
wasn't a coincidence, was it?

574
00:44:39,803 --> 00:44:44,305
You were just pretending to be on her side
while working with Bang Geul this whole time?

575
00:44:44,305 --> 00:44:46,640
Did you play all of us?

576
00:44:50,689 --> 00:44:53,514
Makes things easier that you catch on so fast.

577
00:44:56,634 --> 00:44:58,695
He probably won't answer.

578
00:44:58,695 --> 00:45:01,155
Chairman Na is going through hell right now.

579
00:45:02,667 --> 00:45:05,059
<i>Breaking news. The suspected murderer</i>

580
00:45:05,059 --> 00:45:07,094
[Hospital CCTV Footage]
<i>of the late Chairman Kang of Choiseong Group</i>

581
00:45:07,094 --> 00:45:09,142
<i>is believed to be his daughter-in-law, Ms. Na,</i>

582
00:45:09,142 --> 00:45:10,921
<i>sending shockwaves through the public.</i>

583
00:45:10,921 --> 00:45:14,112
<i>With clear footage of her face now released,</i>

584
00:45:14,112 --> 00:45:17,037
<i>the fallout
surrounding the late Chairman Kang's death</i>

585
00:45:17,037 --> 00:45:20,074
<i>is expected to grow.</i>

586
00:45:20,074 --> 00:45:23,277
If you don't want to get arrested
like Secretary Jo,

587
00:45:23,277 --> 00:45:25,646
it's every man for himself from now on.

588
00:45:31,834 --> 00:45:34,021
Then did you guys take the slush fund, too?

589
00:45:35,767 --> 00:45:37,858
Is this why you brought me here
in the first place?

590
00:45:37,858 --> 00:45:39,727
To trap me in a foreign country?

591
00:45:39,727 --> 00:45:41,728
Hwang Jun Hyeon, you bastard!

592
00:45:43,897 --> 00:45:45,933
Instead of playing the victim,

593
00:45:45,933 --> 00:45:47,934
you should be on your knees
begging Bang Geul for forgiveness,

594
00:45:47,934 --> 00:45:50,971
admitting you're a monster
who committed a deadly sin.

595
00:45:52,606 --> 00:45:57,423
Do you even realize what you've done
just to catch the killer of a dead old man?

596
00:46:01,434 --> 00:46:03,951
You think my dad
will let you get away with this?

597
00:46:06,534 --> 00:46:09,022
You still trust your dad, huh?

598
00:46:09,952 --> 00:46:14,261
Will Chairman Na save you,
or will he save Taeha?

599
00:46:18,769 --> 00:46:19,935
[CEO Jeon Jin Hwan, Taeha Energy]

600
00:46:22,937 --> 00:46:24,802
[CEO Shin Yong Ha, Taeha Chemicals]

601
00:46:26,974 --> 00:46:28,435
[Eldest Son, Taeha Construction]

602
00:46:33,380 --> 00:46:34,982
[International Call]

603
00:46:39,134 --> 00:46:40,412
<i>Dad.</i>

604
00:46:40,412 --> 00:46:43,457
Eun Se, are you okay?

605
00:46:43,457 --> 00:46:45,693
[Suspect Believed
to Be Daughter-in-Law, Ms. Na]

606
00:46:46,467 --> 00:46:50,497
There's no way Mr. Hwang leaked the video
without consulting me first.

607
00:46:51,634 --> 00:46:53,934
What on earth is going on?

608
00:46:56,300 --> 00:46:57,771
Chairman.

609
00:47:23,497 --> 00:47:25,435
[Choiseong: The Future of New Business]

610
00:47:26,267 --> 00:47:28,902
That despicable monster!

611
00:47:30,901 --> 00:47:34,072
Eun Se is no longer a daughter of mine.

612
00:47:34,072 --> 00:47:36,911
I'll drag her in myself,
expose her crimes to the world,

613
00:47:36,911 --> 00:47:39,446
and make sure she gets what she deserves.

614
00:47:40,250 --> 00:47:42,953
You must have been through so much.

615
00:47:42,953 --> 00:47:45,956
Your father and I were old friends
before we became in-laws.

616
00:47:45,956 --> 00:47:49,025
I don't even know how to ask
the deceased for forgiveness.

617
00:47:49,025 --> 00:47:51,125
If failing to keep a married daughter in line

618
00:47:51,125 --> 00:47:53,227
and being blind to all this
until it got to this point

619
00:47:53,227 --> 00:47:54,398
is a sin, then I am a sinner.

620
00:47:54,398 --> 00:47:58,532
Let me apologize... in her place.

621
00:48:10,068 --> 00:48:12,315
There are too many eyes here.

622
00:48:12,315 --> 00:48:14,648
Let's take this somewhere private.

623
00:48:16,785 --> 00:48:18,585
Chairman Na Byeong Mo.

624
00:48:20,090 --> 00:48:24,025
Your daughter, Na Eun Se,
left for Singapore yesterday, didn't she?

625
00:48:24,025 --> 00:48:25,967
I have no intention
of covering up my daughter's crimes,

626
00:48:25,967 --> 00:48:28,225
and I'll cooperate fully.

627
00:48:28,225 --> 00:48:29,586
As soon as she's back in Korea...

628
00:48:29,586 --> 00:48:33,770
Didn't you help her flee the country
to launder your slush fund?

629
00:48:33,770 --> 00:48:35,160
What?

630
00:48:37,004 --> 00:48:38,372
[Police for the People]
<i>Excuse me,</i>

631
00:48:38,372 --> 00:48:41,244
<i>where is the Anti-Corruption
and Economic Crime Investigation Unit?</i>

632
00:48:41,244 --> 00:48:43,069
<i>Just head this way.</i>

633
00:48:48,315 --> 00:48:50,829
[Taeha Group Chairman Na Byeong Mo's
Slush Fund Records]

634
00:48:51,688 --> 00:48:53,954
<i>Hot delivery coming through!</i>

635
00:48:53,954 --> 00:48:55,867
[Anti-Corruption
and Economic Crime Investigation Unit]

636
00:48:55,867 --> 00:48:57,400
Do you have any idea

637
00:48:57,400 --> 00:49:00,249
how many people try to drag me down
with false tips like that?

638
00:49:00,249 --> 00:49:03,309
Then you must know Ham Du Ho, right?

639
00:49:03,309 --> 00:49:05,102
He worked security
at Hangang University Hospital,

640
00:49:05,102 --> 00:49:07,103
and he died recently.

641
00:49:09,036 --> 00:49:10,650
Murdered, to be exact.

642
00:49:10,650 --> 00:49:14,445
And we have evidence
suggesting you ordered the hit.

643
00:49:14,445 --> 00:49:15,576
What a load of nonsense!

644
00:49:15,576 --> 00:49:18,345
<i>He contacted you too, right?</i>

645
00:49:19,036 --> 00:49:21,849
<i>There's another video
on the security guard's phone?</i>

646
00:49:21,849 --> 00:49:25,055
<i>Said he'd tell you the truth
if you paid enough.</i>

647
00:49:25,055 --> 00:49:28,056
<i>He got too greedy.</i>

648
00:49:28,056 --> 00:49:29,756
<i>Don't you think?</i>

649
00:49:30,761 --> 00:49:33,576
<i>Turns out he had
a hidden camera in his glasses.</i>

650
00:49:33,576 --> 00:49:37,434
<i>It recorded everything,
including Secretary Jo bribing him</i>

651
00:49:37,434 --> 00:49:39,001
<i>to steal the hospital CCTV footage.</i>

652
00:49:39,001 --> 00:49:43,607
<i>Let's show the world
who Na Byeong Mo really is,</i>

653
00:49:43,607 --> 00:49:45,272
<i>Sang Jae.</i>

654
00:49:46,634 --> 00:49:49,124
That's not my voice.

655
00:49:49,124 --> 00:49:52,224
Someone must have doctored it,
just like Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong's recording.

656
00:49:52,224 --> 00:49:54,985
My secretary acted on his own
out of some twisted loyalty,

657
00:49:54,985 --> 00:49:56,325
and now he's pinning it on me!

658
00:49:56,325 --> 00:49:59,767
We'll see about that
when we get you two in the same room.

659
00:49:59,767 --> 00:50:01,200
We've also put out a red notice,

660
00:50:01,200 --> 00:50:03,624
so you'll be reuniting
with your daughter very soon.

661
00:50:03,624 --> 00:50:05,034
I didn't know anything!

662
00:50:05,034 --> 00:50:06,925
I am innocent!

663
00:50:06,925 --> 00:50:09,734
Take your hands off me!

664
00:50:09,734 --> 00:50:11,565
Are you kidding me right now?

665
00:50:16,495 --> 00:50:19,907
<i>Following a surprise raid on Taeha Group,</i>

666
00:50:19,907 --> 00:50:23,544
<i>police are tracking down
the 300 billion won corporate loan</i>

667
00:50:23,544 --> 00:50:25,913
<i>Taeha took out to ostensibly acquire</i>

668
00:50:25,913 --> 00:50:27,981
<i>Choiseong Trading's hydrogen rights,</i>

669
00:50:27,981 --> 00:50:30,417
<i>which they stole without paying the balance.</i>

670
00:50:30,417 --> 00:50:33,954
<i>Authorities also plan
to work closely with Singapore,</i>

671
00:50:33,954 --> 00:50:37,891
<i>where Chairman Na allegedly
hid his slush funds.</i>

672
00:50:40,194 --> 00:50:44,565
<i>Meanwhile, the whereabouts
of Na Eun Se, the prime suspect</i>

673
00:50:44,565 --> 00:50:47,201
<i>in the murder of late Choiseong Chairman Kang,
remain unknown.</i>

674
00:50:47,201 --> 00:50:50,604
<i>Chairman Na, currently under investigation,</i>

675
00:50:50,604 --> 00:50:54,274
<i>has reportedly stated that</i>

676
00:50:54,274 --> 00:50:56,267
<i>his daughter acted entirely on her own.</i>

677
00:50:56,267 --> 00:50:58,834
<i>Eun Se is no longer a daughter of mine.</i>

678
00:50:58,834 --> 00:51:01,682
<i>I'll drag her in myself,
expose her crimes to the world,</i>

679
00:51:01,682 --> 00:51:04,151
<i>and make sure she gets what she deserves.</i>

680
00:51:06,101 --> 00:51:07,567
<i>Eun Se,</i>

681
00:51:07,567 --> 00:51:08,901
<i>are you okay?</i>

682
00:51:08,901 --> 00:51:10,527
<i>We got completely played.</i>

683
00:51:10,527 --> 00:51:11,461
<i>Hwang Jun Hyeon, that bastard...</i>

684
00:51:11,461 --> 00:51:13,894
<i>Don't come back to Korea for a while.</i>

685
00:51:15,062 --> 00:51:16,096
<i>What?</i>

686
00:51:16,096 --> 00:51:20,567
<i>Go straight to Florida
and lay low at the villa.</i>

687
00:51:20,567 --> 00:51:21,703
<i>Dad...</i>

688
00:51:21,703 --> 00:51:24,441
<i>It's the best way to do damage control.</i>

689
00:51:24,441 --> 00:51:26,607
<i>Without hard evidence or a suspect,</i>

690
00:51:26,607 --> 00:51:28,809
<i>the investigation will just fizzle out.</i>

691
00:51:28,809 --> 00:51:31,300
<i>Just do as you're told for now.</i>

692
00:51:31,300 --> 00:51:33,316
<i>That's how we both survive.</i>

693
00:51:33,316 --> 00:51:35,783
<i>You hear me?</i>

694
00:51:35,783 --> 00:51:37,503
<i>Eun Se.</i>

695
00:51:37,503 --> 00:51:38,663
<i>Eun Se!</i>

696
00:51:38,663 --> 00:51:40,754
<i>Na Eun Se!</i>

697
00:51:40,754 --> 00:51:43,767
<i>He sounds desperate for a guy
selling out his own daughter.</i>

698
00:51:43,767 --> 00:51:44,967
<i>Shut up.</i>

699
00:51:44,967 --> 00:51:46,483
<i>Fine.</i>

700
00:51:46,483 --> 00:51:48,695
<i>Go ahead and play the martyr.</i>

701
00:51:48,695 --> 00:51:50,634
<i>Take the fall for him all by yourself.</i>

702
00:51:50,634 --> 00:51:52,766
<i>I said shut up!</i>

703
00:52:11,475 --> 00:52:15,349
It's either she goes down,
or she takes her father down.

704
00:52:15,349 --> 00:52:17,310
Must be quite the dilemma for her.

705
00:52:17,310 --> 00:52:19,150
She just watched him throw her to the wolves.

706
00:52:19,150 --> 00:52:21,828
She's probably just figuring out
how to take him down.

707
00:52:31,333 --> 00:52:32,609
Yes, Chairman.

708
00:52:32,609 --> 00:52:34,801
Why are you so hard to reach?

709
00:52:34,801 --> 00:52:37,148
I just landed.

710
00:52:37,148 --> 00:52:38,928
I'll head straight back to the office.

711
00:52:38,928 --> 00:52:41,284
We have a lot to talk about.

712
00:52:41,284 --> 00:52:43,483
Alright.

713
00:52:47,934 --> 00:52:49,788
Can I get you something to eat?

714
00:52:49,788 --> 00:52:51,248
You haven't had dinner yet.

715
00:52:51,248 --> 00:52:53,414
I'm not hungry.

716
00:52:53,414 --> 00:52:55,408
You should head home too.

717
00:52:55,408 --> 00:52:57,767
And tell the task force to call it a day.

718
00:52:57,767 --> 00:52:59,199
Well...

719
00:53:09,635 --> 00:53:11,878
Did Jae Seong leave for the day?

720
00:53:35,567 --> 00:53:37,367
Call me if anything happens.

721
00:53:37,367 --> 00:53:39,209
Don't try to be a hero.

722
00:53:39,209 --> 00:53:41,208
Stop nagging and get going.

723
00:53:41,208 --> 00:53:43,773
Call me, no matter how late it is.

724
00:53:43,773 --> 00:53:45,245
Got it?

725
00:53:47,748 --> 00:53:50,083
Please drive safely.

726
00:53:51,113 --> 00:53:52,886
You promised, okay?

727
00:55:03,701 --> 00:55:06,571
Not enough evidence?

728
00:55:06,571 --> 00:55:09,451
Or just a killer legal team?

729
00:55:09,451 --> 00:55:12,135
Didn't expect you to be out this fast.

730
00:55:12,135 --> 00:55:15,391
I am the head
of a major conglomerate, after all.

731
00:55:15,391 --> 00:55:17,140
Though I admit, I was surprised myself.

732
00:55:17,140 --> 00:55:20,473
It's the first time
I've been stabbed in the back this hard.

733
00:55:26,701 --> 00:55:31,655
You stabbed your own daughter in the back
just to save your own neck.

734
00:55:31,655 --> 00:55:32,667
Cut the bullshit.

735
00:55:32,667 --> 00:55:34,320
What?

736
00:55:36,367 --> 00:55:39,526
That stench doesn't wash off easily, does it?

737
00:55:40,627 --> 00:55:45,866
Doesn't matter how much designer crap you wear
or how fancy your chair is.

738
00:55:45,866 --> 00:55:48,235
Your filthy habits never change.

739
00:55:48,235 --> 00:55:49,836
You little bastard!

740
00:55:54,034 --> 00:55:59,326
That look in your eyes,
running your mouth with zero fear...

741
00:55:59,326 --> 00:56:01,915
you're exactly like him.

742
00:56:02,801 --> 00:56:04,984
Don't you recognize me?

743
00:56:06,010 --> 00:56:07,654
It's me.

744
00:56:08,534 --> 00:56:11,291
Kang Yong Ho. The man you murdered.

745
00:56:17,101 --> 00:56:21,896
You knew you couldn't beat me
unless you killed me!

746
00:56:21,896 --> 00:56:23,570
Aren't you ashamed?

747
00:56:23,570 --> 00:56:25,772
Causing all this chaos
just to plant a flag on my grave

748
00:56:25,772 --> 00:56:28,074
and pat yourself on the back?

749
00:56:29,967 --> 00:56:32,312
Glory is fleeting,
and it all ends when you die.

750
00:56:32,312 --> 00:56:33,984
What more could you possibly want?

751
00:56:33,984 --> 00:56:35,748
You little prick!

752
00:56:37,734 --> 00:56:41,021
You think I don't see right through you?

753
00:56:41,021 --> 00:56:46,493
Using naive Bang Geul to swallow up Choiseong
out of some petty revenge? I respect that.

754
00:56:46,493 --> 00:56:51,034
I like that kind of ambition.

755
00:56:51,034 --> 00:56:55,935
Too bad... you're not on my side.

756
00:57:05,901 --> 00:57:07,914
Say hi...

757
00:57:08,600 --> 00:57:10,617
to Kang Yong Ho for me.

758
00:57:45,333 --> 00:57:47,587
Why is he calling instead of coming up?

759
00:57:55,932 --> 00:57:58,402
[Dad]

760
00:58:06,773 --> 00:58:08,847
[Missed call: Dad]

761
00:58:21,434 --> 00:58:24,903
<i>You ruled the world long enough, didn't you?</i>

762
00:58:24,903 --> 00:58:27,367
<i>How long are you going to block my path?</i>

763
00:58:27,367 --> 00:58:29,590
<i>What's still holding you here?</i>

764
00:58:29,590 --> 00:58:33,433
<i>Should I... end it for you?</i>

765
00:59:05,966 --> 00:59:10,402
[Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong]

766
00:59:30,127 --> 00:59:31,987
Dad...

